workout_explanation: This workout plan prioritizes compound movements for the triceps, focusing on different heads of the muscle to ensure comprehensive development. The exercises are ordered to maximize efficiency and minimize rest time. The volume is tailored to an intermediate user with a 45-minute time constraint, adhering to the guidelines from the provided wikis. The moderate volume and rep ranges are chosen to promote hypertrophy while preventing overtraining.  The inclusion of both overhead and pressing movements ensures a balanced approach, targeting all three heads of the triceps. Alternative exercises are provided for flexibility and to cater to individual preferences and equipment availability.
